Compliance Hold\". R6: Politically Exposed Persons (PEPs) are subject to mandatory SOW-Enhanced verification regardless of transaction size.",
      "summary": "Prohibited industries include crypto, cannabis, gambling, and unlicensed arms dealing; all transactions to crypto gateways automatically blocked. All initial deposits require SOW declaration; business sales and inheritances require specific documentation. PEPs require mandatory SOW-Enhanced verification.",
